          <lg n="1">
            <l xml:id="swift-980-002D-line-1" n="1">Dear Tom, I'm surpriz'd that Your Verse did not jingle</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-980-002D-line-2" n="2">But Your Rhyme was not double, cause y<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> sight was but single</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-980-002D-line-3" n="3">For as Helsham observes there's nothing can Chyme,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-980-002D-line-4" n="4">Or fit more Exact than One Eye and One Rhyme.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-980-002D-line-5" n="5">If You had not took Physick, I'd pay off Your Bacon</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-980-002D-line-6" n="6">But now I'll write short, for fear You're short taken.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-980-002D-line-7" n="7">Besides Dick forbid me, and call'd me a Fool</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-980-002D-line-8" n="8">For he says short as 'tis it will give You a stool.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-980-002D-line-9" n="9"><lb/>In Libris bellis tu parum parcis ocellis</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-980-002D-line-10" n="10">Dum nimium scribis, Vel Talpâ cæcior ibis,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-980-002D-line-11" n="11">Aut ad Vina redis, nam sic tua Lumina Lædis.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-980-002D-line-12" n="12">Sed tibi Cœnanti sunt Collyria tanti?</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-980-002D-line-13" n="13">Nunquid eges Visu d\u·<hi rend="italics">over</hi>·a\m comples omnia risu?</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-980-002D-line-14" n="14">Heu! Sheridan cæcus, heu eris nunc Circopithecus</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-980-002D-line-15" n="15">Nunc bene Nasutus mittet tibi carmina tutus,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-980-002D-line-16" n="16">Nunc ope Burgundi malus Helsham ridet Abunde</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-980-002D-line-17" n="17">Nec Phœbi fili Versum <note place="foot">·pro potes Hor:.</note> <hi rend="italics">quis</hi> mittere Ryly</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-980-002D-line-18" n="18">Quid Tibi cum Libris, relavet tua Lumina <note place="foot">·pro quovis fluvio: Virg:.</note> Tybris</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-980-002D-line-19" n="19">Mixtus <note place="foot">·Sacⁿharo saturni.</note> Saturno, penso sed parce diurno</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-980-002D-line-20" n="20">Observes hoc tu, nec scriptis utere noctu.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-980-002D-line-21" n="21">Nonnulli mingunt, et palpebras sibi tingunt</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-980-002D-line-22" n="22">Quidam purgantes, libros in stercore nantes</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-980-002D-line-23" n="23">Linqunt, sic Vinces, Videndo, mi bone Lynces.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-980-002D-line-24" n="24">Culum Oculum tergis, dum scripta hoc flumine mergis.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-980-002D-line-25" n="25">Tunc Oculi et Nates, ni fallor agent tibi grates.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-980-002D-line-26" n="26">Vim fuge Decani, nec sit tibi cura Delani,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-980-002D-line-27" n="27">Heu tibi si scribant, aut si tibi fercula libant</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-980-002D-line-28" n="28">Pone loco Mortis Rupis fera pocula fortis,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-980-002D-line-29" n="29">Hæc tibi pauca dedi, sed Consule Betty Mi Lady,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-980-002D-line-30" n="30">Huic te des Solæ, nec Egebis Pharmacapolæ.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-980-002D-line-31" n="31">«LD»Hæc somnians cecini</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-980-002D-line-32" n="32">
              <space>Octob: 23<hi rend="superscript">d</hi>/hi&gt; 1718</space>
            </l>
            <l xml:id="swift-980-002D-line-33" n="33">
              <space>J<hi rend="superscript">n</hi>/hi&gt;: Swift.</space>
            </l>
